 xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 24, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zzv1665703197960.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zzv1665703197960.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zzv1665703197960.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zzv1665703197960\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                           \n UROUTER_SHUT \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Shut down the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__topic_d135509e1_d135510e1_d135511e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d135512e1_d135513e1_d135514e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">operation UROUTER_SHUT</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">string</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mode</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C1)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">string</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C80)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__section_nxk_lx1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d480706e85\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__ul_sqp_mx1_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__li_d48089e1_d48090e1_d48091e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mode</var> is the stop-mode: <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code> for forced or\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">N</code> for normal. <p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d135518e1_d135519e1_d135520e1\">In forced mode,\n            all servers are stopped, clients are disconnected, and the Uniface Router exits. In\n            normal mode, existing clients are allowed to deliver requests to servers until the\n            server reports it has no state, that is, it has no locks and no context (active\n            component instances). At that moment the server is stopped. Once all the servers are\n            stopped, the remaining clients are disconnected and the Uniface Router exits.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__li_d48092e1_d48093e1_d48094e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var> is a message that is displayed in all running monitors and is\n          returned to new clients or monitors that are refused connections. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__section_l2d_tr1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d480706e115\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d134921e1_d134922e1_d134923e1\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to 0.\n        Otherwise, see the \"Return Codes\" section in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html\" title=\"UROUTMON is an internal component that enables you to write your own Uniface Router monitor to access and modify the Uniface Router's parameters and settings.\">UROUTMON</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__section_yh1_qx1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d480706e134\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d135212e1_d135213e1_d135214e1\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__section_ohf_rx1_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d480706e143\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d135536e1_d135537e1_d135538e1\">The privileged-user operation\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">UROUTER_SHUT</span> shuts down the Uniface Router in normal or forced mode.\n        All new connection requests are refused and no new servers will be started.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zzv1665703197960__p_d135539e1_d135540e1_d135541e1\">This operation returns once the request is posted at\n        the Uniface Router. This operation might fail if the Uniface Router is already shutting down\n        at an equal or higher mode.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UROUTER_SHUT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 24, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 UROUTER_SHUT Shut down the Uniface Router. operation UROUTER_SHUT params string Mode : IN ; (C1) string Message : IN ; (C80) endparams Parameters Mode is the stop-mode: F for forced or N for normal. In forced mode, all servers are stopped, clients are disconnected, and the Uniface Router exits. In normal mode, existing clients are allowed to deliver requests to servers until the server reports it has no state, that is, it has no locks and no context (active component instances). At that moment the server is stopped. Once all the servers are stopped, the remaining clients are disconnected and the Uniface Router exits. Message is a message that is displayed in all running monitors and is returned to new clients or monitors that are refused connections. Return Values If successful, $status is set to 0. Otherwise, see the \"Return Codes\" section in UROUTMON . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The privileged-user operation UROUTER_SHUT shuts down the Uniface Router in normal or forced mode. All new connection requests are refused and no new servers will be started. This operation returns once the request is posted at the Uniface Router. This operation might fail if the Uniface Router is already shutting down at an equal or higher mode. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}